Tags:

docker run redis:4.0

STDIN:
(Interactive)
docker run -i kodekloud/simple-prompt-docker
(psudo terminal) with prompt 
docker run -it kodekloud/simple-prompt-docker
(Running a Ubuntu image and "get in")
docker run -it ubuntu bash

Port mapping:
docker run -p 80:5000 kodekcloud/webapp
(Mapping localhost:80 to docker host internal port 5000)

Volume/directory mapping:
docker run -v /opt/datadir:/var/lib/mysql mysql
(Computer directory : docker internal directory)

Inspect container:
docker inspect blissful_hopper

Container logs:
docker logs blissful_hopper 

ENV Variable:
Docker run -e